rating_comment: The place is pretty awesome and surrounding including the lake view is amazing. I will highly recommend this place and will always consider this place during our next visit. Faraaz is very helpful along with the entire house helping staffs. We had a small issue which was fixed in some 10 minutes, that's where I was very much satisfied for booking this place for our stay.

info: Rating, 3 stars,  · January 2023,  · Stayed about a week
rating_comment:
It is a fairly new building and new furniture but really bad maintenance. Floor is dirty. Kitchen floor, counter, stove etc never properly clean. Accumulation of dirtiness is everywhere in the kitchen. Bathroom floor and wall needs deep cleaning each time after customers leave. Location is next to dirty lake cause more mosquitoes than other locations. Summer might be real danger for mosquitoes related disease.
Staffs were very nice and owner communicated very promptly.

rating_comment: The apartment is just near a river and each time when I go to the balcony I will see a picturesque which I feel so unrealistic. The house has a excellent location: it is near the main streets but I haven’t feel noisy because of the barrier of the river. Owner of the house responses quickly and for every inquiry and asking for help, he always respond with 5 minutes and solve the problem as soon as possible. In one word, it is a comfortable and unforgettable experience.
